{"tid":100020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昆明機場檢走大量偽裝違禁品","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T15:57:26.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4d429d311eadcb8fed67072a1251a383464038","tid":100020,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/620529661472439/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F620529661472439%2F&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8bbf02e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/620529661472439/</a><br />\n【帶上航機違禁品千奇百怪】<br />\n<br />\n每年春運期間，內地機場的安檢人員都會截到很多違禁帶上飛機的物品。<br />\n<br />\n在雲南昆明長水國際機場，旅客花盡心思意圖帶上飛機的違禁物品，包括有偽裝成筆的刀具，看似是智能電話的打火機，甚至電鑽、 鐵鎚等。<br />\n<br />\n查獲的物品，多到足以開一間雜貨鋪。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#機場　＃違禁品　有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}